snippet.title: MouseBot Gameplay - "Platforming Jester"
snippet.description:
MouseBot: Escape from Catlab is coming to mobile platforms everywhere on April 4!

Even at night the experiments in CatLab continue.  Wath out for those water mines!

Get the game here:  http://onelink.to/mbot-vu
